{"tid":1614867,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國二戰轟炸機迫降機場時墜毀　造成7死6傷","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:19:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:19:04.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f664a029e0ded46f45fe2e41e8cd28b86cd19c6c","tid":1614867,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"美國一架二戰時期的轟炸機，在康涅狄格州機場迫降時墜毀，造成7人死亡，6人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地星期三，當局說，這架載有13人的B-17轟炸機，起飛後不久出現問題，需要緊急折返，但降落時在跑道失控，撞向維修設備及除冰劑的貯存缸，飛機著火焚燒，黑煙升上半空。<br />\n<br />\n受事故影響，機場關閉大約3個半小時，當局正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483996-20191003.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483996-20191003.htm&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7EBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=10a9ff62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483996-20191003.htm&h=6fa83a89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483996-20191003.htm</a>"}]}